25bb%25e5%25bd%25b1%25e7%25af%2580%25e3%2580%258d%25e7%258d%25b2%25e7%258d%258e&h=4975c142\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200423/s00001/1587635379123/%e3%80%8a%e9%8f%97%e9%8f%98%e9%9b%86%e3%80%8b-now%e6%96%b0%e8%81%9e%e3%80%8a%e7%b6%93%e7%b7%af%e7%b7%9a%e3%80%8b%e5%8f%8d%e4%bf%ae%e4%be%8b7-21%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97%e7%af%80%e7%9b%ae-%e3%80%8c%e7%b4%90%e7%b4%84%e9%9b%bb%e8%a6%96%e9%9b%bb%e5%bd%b1%e7%af%80%e3%80%8d%e7%8d%b2%e7%8d%8e</a><br />\n<br />\n去年反修例風波，香港上演一幕幕歷史場面。「2020年紐約電視電影節」得獎名單公布，香港電台《鏗鏘集》及now新聞台《經緯線》分別憑反修例、7．21元朗事件有關節目等獲獎。<br />\n<br />\n奪得5個獎項的《鏗鏘集》，憑《721元朗黑夜》 奪得最佳新聞調查報道優異獎；與年輕抗爭者有關的《這年初夏》及《這一年&hellip;十五歲的暑假》，則獲頒最佳新聞跟進報道優異獎。<br />\n<br />\n獲頒3個獎項的now新聞台《經緯線》，憑《元朗黑夜》贏得最佳新聞紀錄片優異獎；有關反修例抗爭中社工、義務急救員的《同路人》，則奪得最佳公共事務節目銀獎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200423/s00001/80b614d6095fe36722951b3601f28bd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200423%2Fs00001%2F80b614d6095fe36722951b3601f28bd8.jpg&h=79f0dc5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>你條撚樣成撚日話成日spin 7.21係fake news，點知外國唔係咁睇，關於7.21既全部都拎獎</strong></span>"},{"pid":"b4ab45772eba613997cbc09849d367f0f42d2d44","tid":1985964,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:49:15.000Z","msg":"自推下"},{"pid":"e40254abed8a436af5cc3a34ecf6029ddbee91d8","tid":1985964,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:56:35.000Z","msg":"梗係啦有300萬收視既何已完做男主"},{"pid":"87b21c37340154cd0fe18819a7450f651df33074","tid":1985964,"uid":145292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcd87239c2e88917ecdf40c4278f0320a39bfa9","tid":1985964,"uid":156096,"like":0,